<li>I am so deeply sorry to hear about the passing of your (mother/father/sibling/etc.).  My thoughts and prayers are with you all.</li>
<li>Words cannot express how saddened I am by your loss.  Please know that I'm here for you if you need anything at all.</li>
<li>Sending you my heartfelt sympathy and love.  May your treasured memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>Your family is in my thoughts and prayers during this incredibly painful time.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy, I offer my condolences on your loss.  May your hearts find peace.</li>
<li>I was so sorry to hear of your loss.  May happy memories ease the pain.</li>
<li>Thinking of your family and sending my love and support during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Please accept my heartfelt condolences on the passing of your beloved (name).</li>
<li>May the love and support of your family help ease your sorrow. My deepest condolences.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and love as you navigate this difficult journey.</li>
<li>My heart goes out to you and your family. I am here for you if you need anything.</li>
<li>I am so sorry for your loss and will keep you all in my prayers.</li>
<li>May the beautiful memories you shared bring you comfort in the coming days.</li>
<li>Sending you all my love and support during this heartbreaking time.</li>
    

